OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FWarm away from eastern coasts,
OL,6,Fwith the Central Belt seasonally very
OL,7,Fwarm. Most dry with sunny spells which
OL,8,Fturn hazy during the afternoon as
OL,9,Fhigher cloud increases. Southeast
OL,10,Fwinds fresh around coasts.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FCloud thickening to bring
OL,13,Fsome patchy rain, this focused west of
OL,14,Fthe M74, with little expected to
OL,15,Fpenetrate to the east coast. Southerly
OL,16,Fcoastal winds initially fresh.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
