OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F179A1775537898
OL,1,Wj5hw1~{4k7juhw1{$             G2/2
OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FEastern coastal areas
OL,6,Fmilder than today. Elsewhere
OL,7,Fsignificantly cooler. Rather cloudy
OL,8,Fmorning with some patchy light rain,
OL,9,Fmostly confined to the west. Mainly
OL,10,Fdry for afternoon with brighter spells.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FRain
OL,13,Fearly Thursday, clearing to brighter
OL,14,Fspells and showers for afternoon.
OL,15,FFriday wet and windy with best of
OL,16,Fshelter in east. Blustery showers
OL,17,FSaturday, heavier and more frequent in
OL,18,Fwest.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
